mitche: We have a bit of time left over - we can either play some, or I can bore you with a discussion of something useful - like bidding over takeout doubles
OK - doubles and responding:

When your left-hand opponent opens the bidding and your partner doubles, it shows support (at least Hxx) for any unbid major. 
And shortness in the suit that she doubled.|
