Basically the rule of 12 is: 
- the length of your trump suit plus the level of the contract must be at least 12 (rule of 12)
- And the number of trump winners in your hand + level is at least 10

So here, you have 3 sure winners (KQ109) and the opponents are contracting for 7 tricks.. (rule of 10)
You have a misfit and the balance of power: you have 5 trumps + 7 trick contract level = 12, 
3 trump tricks + 7 tricks = 10|
