LHO bids 1@d  X  2@d  ???
You would double again - especially if I get the hand right Qxxx, Axxx, xx, QJx 
So a responsive double shows support for any suit the doubler would like to bid... 
If the auction were 1@s  X  2@s, you would need a hand like this to double responsively: 
xx, Axxx, KJx, QJxx|
